# Desktop env vars are provided by the root dotenvx config.
# When running `pnpm dev` from the repo root, dotenvx decrypts .env.local
# and sets SUPABASE_URL / SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY as process.env vars.
# Vite's `define` block in vite.config.ts maps them to VITE_* for the renderer.
#
# No local .env file is needed in this directory.
#
# Required root env vars:
#   SUPABASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:54321
#   SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=<your-publishable-key-from-supabase-status>
